Module portsim.app.main
Package portsim.util

Class BadEncodingException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • portsim.util.BadEncodingException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class BadEncodingException
extends java.lang.Exception
    Exception thrown when an encoded string is not correct according to the appropriate fromString() method.
    Also contains a handful of useful static methods used within the fromStrings.
    See Also:
